                     <interp inst="t17890422-6-off20" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17890422-6-off20" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17890422-6-cd21" type="crimeDate">11th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890422-6-off20 t17890422-6-cd21"></join>, a silver watch, value 40 s. a steel chain, value 6 d. a stone seal, set in silver, value 3 s. and a metal watch-key, value 1 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17890422-6-victim98" type="victimName">
                     Richard 
                     Saunders
                  <interp inst="t17890422-6-victim98" type="surname" value="Saunders"></interp>
